getVerb

public String getVerb(int tense,
                      boolean sing,
                      boolean q)
Used to get a verb in the desired tense, language, and number.

Parameters:
tense - An int value used to distinguish the tense to which the verb is to be conjugated.
sing - A boolean value representing whether the subject is singular or plural; true : singular, false : plural.
q - A boolean value representing the language; true : Quenya, false : English.
Returns:
The verb in the desired language, conjugated to the specified tense, agreeing with a subject of the specified number.
